  <ThingDef Name="NCLMechDinergateSniper" ParentName="BaseMechanoidWalker">
    <defName>NCL_Mech_DinergateSniper</defName>
    <label>Dinergate Sniper</label>
<description>Unit Archive: NCL-02 "Dinergate Sniper"
Origin: "Iron Law" Mass-Production Series

A lightweight variant optimized for mid-range engagement. Its compact size enables precise strikes and prolonged reconnaissance. Primary weapon is the 'NCL-42 Red Needle' tactical rifle firing low-cost red ceramic slugs, capable of penetrating 25mm homogeneous steel. Mounts a foldable drone pod for deploying defensive drones at critical moments. Uniquely quiet during operation, it employs erratic repositioning jumps, making it an unpredictable marksman unit. Tactical records indicate its role as the scout and first-strike element preceding main forces.</description>
